column2: SELECT p.SpecObjID, p.photoRa, p.photoDec, p.z, p.zerr, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr FROM SpecPhotoAll AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid=p.objid WHERE photoRa BETWEEN # AND # AND photoDec BETWEEN # AND # AND p.class=&&& AND (p.petromag_r-extinction_r) < # AND p.subClass=&&& AND p.zWarning=# AND p.survey = &&& and p.programname = &&&
